			.panel-heading 
				h3.panel-title Drop Caps (inside Bootstrap panel)
			.panel-body
				p.typl8-drop-cap Then there's the always impressive, drop-cap <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"></span>.  Some say it should go the way of the dinosaur.  For me?  Dunno, I still kinda like em!  Especially if they are of the style with those beautiful colors and gold edging and stuff.  Man, those rock! 
		

